---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Psychological Testing | Morning Tide Consulting and Collective"
	description="Comprehensive psychological testing services including ADHD, autism, diagnostic clarification, learning disorders, and personality evaluations."
>
	<main class="page-main">
		<section class="hero-shell mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-8">
			<p class="eyebrow">Psychological Testing</p>
			<h1 class="max-w-4xl text-5xl leading-none text-(--color-ink) sm:text-6xl">In-depth psychological testing for adults and adolescents.</h1>
			<p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-(--color-muted)">
				Morning Tide offers two categories of evaluation services: psychological evaluations for diagnostic questions and psychoeducational evaluations for academic and learning questions. Both are available remotely across 40+ PSYPACT states with rapid report delivery.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-6xl gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
			<a class="section-shell rounded-4xl p-8 block" href="/services/psychological-evaluations">
				<p class="eyebrow">Psychological Evaluations</p>
				<h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl leading-none text-(--color-ink)">Diagnostic clarity for complex clinical presentations.</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-(--color-muted)">ADHD, autism, diagnostic clarification, learning disorders, and personality assessments using gold-standard tools like the ADOS-2 and MIGDAS-2.</p>
				<span class="mt-6 inline-flex rounded-full bg-(--color-accent) px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-(--color-button-ink) shadow-(--shadow-brand)">View psychological evaluations</span>
			</a>

			<a class="rounded-4xl border border-(--color-line-soft) bg-(--color-surface) p-8 shadow-(--shadow-soft) block" href="/services/psychoeducational-testing">
				<p class="eyebrow">Psychoeducational Evaluations</p>
				<h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl leading-none text-(--color-ink)">Answers for learning, school planning, and academic questions.</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-(--color-muted)">Dyslexia, learning disorders, giftedness, academic achievement, and twice-exceptional (2E) testing with school-ready reports and actionable recommendations.</p>
				<span class="mt-6 inline-flex rounded-full border border-(--color-line) bg-(--color-surface) px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-(--color-ink)">View psychoeducational evaluations</span>
			</a>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
